          <p>河合第三回記述　<span>B判定</span>→→不合格</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contents-item">
          <img src="https://www.yotsuyagakuin.com/b_geneki/wp/wp-content/uploads/tokyo-u_main_image.jpg">
